<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="8431323">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8431323/" class="title-link">接地气的论方法</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8431323"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/lolisary/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1268152-8.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/lolisary/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">迷路的埃及猫|记住，我是个疯子</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2017-03-22"
      class="main-meta">2017-03-22 22:49:41</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8431323_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这本社会学研究方法专业书可说是读过的最好的，好在无比接地气。 基于30年的社会学研究实践和不断的追问反思深挖，不仅论了方法，写通透了在做社会学研究时该怎样实际操作，从实际案例和亲身经验出发论清了实践中使用的方法的方法论，更还基于对研究弱势人群和敏感问题的思考和...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_8431323_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_8431323_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










